<h3>Labor</h3>
<p>Labor for a 25-square architectural asphalt reroof typically runs 3–5 crew-days of work. At U.S. loaded labor rates of $45–$85/hour for skilled roofers depending on market, total labor cost runs $3,500–$8,500 for the install portion alone.</p>
<h3>Tear-off and disposal</h3>
<p>Tearing off an existing asphalt roof adds $1–$3 per square foot ($1,000–$2,000 for a 2,000 sq ft roof) plus dump fees. Dump fees vary enormously by market:</p>
